---
description: Agent Cost usage and budget tracking rules
globs: **/*
alwaysApply: false
---

Use Agent Cost when AI usage or model cost matters.

- Record provider, model, task, owner, date, and reason.
- Mark estimated values clearly.
- Do not store API keys, invoice originals, or payment details.
- Run `node .opendock/harness/opendock__agent-cost/check.mjs` before handoff when possible.
